{"tid":1924581,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"其實外國唔俾人戴口罩個風氣真係好on9","createTime":"2020-03-13T18:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T23:33:58.000Z","uid":74403,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8559f12caa233549566b2aa4dc38d265429d839b","tid":1924581,"uid":74403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:31:36.000Z","msg":"外國人成日話戴口罩冇用，<br />\n唔可以幫自己免疫，<br />\n我先唔論戴口罩可唔可以減低自己奶野風險，<br />\n佢地整到個風氣係戴口罩就等於有病，<br />\n咁出街就會俾人歧視，<br />\n咁當我真係有病我都唔撚夠膽戴啦。<br />\n同埋奶左野都可以冇病癥架，<br />\n咁每個人戴返個口罩咪可以保護到每個人囉，<br />\n點解班on9鬼佬咁都諗唔明，<br />\n雖然我覺得係d政府唔夠口罩覺咁講，<br />\n但係d市民唔撚識用個閪腦諗下架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cadae20928d593c5dab0fc317d008bd8288b8b1","tid":1924581,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:34:41.000Z","msg":"根本冇咁多產量"},{"pid":"8abcf31d209b229d20ec7ddf5fe8551e913b7b8a","tid":1924581,"uid":70888,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:39:34.000Z","msg":"事實上大部分鬼佬真係on9同蠢"},{"pid":"3c1ebde51992245e78a98632e864cc55febfe687","tid":1924581,"uid":331822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cadae20928d593c5dab0fc317d008bd8288b8b1","tid":1924581,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:34:41.000Z","msg":"根本冇咁多產量"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:41:23.000Z","msg":"所以要同時降低所有人的活動，例如番工、番學"},{"pid":"ec43b138a20df78bd6024f3d9b889c11c7ca7381","tid":1924581,"uid":81478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:43:30.000Z","msg":"我都唔明點解個風氣咁搞笑<br />\n明明有科學根據 但咁都唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係要奶下嘢先會變得醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74962782289dfbbdab203f672d4c07b6412b5fcc","tid":1924581,"uid":80464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:45:03.000Z","msg":"其實某程度上係因為